{"tid":176152,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"肌肉撚入 想練腹肌求指教","createTime":"2017-03-28T04:01:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T05:38:29.000Z","uid":12286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8c0ccaada1b5e8604adcdf13165317cd1181583b","tid":176152,"uid":12286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:01:05.000Z","msg":"我想練腹肌人魚線<br />\n上網睇到好多練腹肌帶氧操<br />\n但個d本身都已經好撚瘦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我有個肚腩<br />\n係咪一定要減左個肚腩先練到線條?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇本來有肚腩既巴絲最後係練得起個線條?<br />\n<br />\n男女既練法係咪都唔同<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf3b0c7714f2950df7fc3fc8dcb40b338f154870","tid":176152,"uid":97409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:07:16.000Z","msg":"不斷練就得，腹呢個部位可以狂練，做下捲腹、平板或者推滾輪"},{"pid":"5a6981180fab037b7a0b2107a2d47b481aa9c08e","tid":176152,"uid":93486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:07:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想練腹肌人魚線<br />\n上網睇到好多練腹肌帶氧操<br />\n但個d本身都已經好撚瘦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我有個肚腩<br />\n係咪一定要減左個肚腩先練到線條?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇本來有肚腩既巴絲最後係練得起個線條?<br />\n<br />\n男女既練法係咪都唔同<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n報力威啦"},{"pid":"7191627f6539cff31fafd348a57b081a716d5b79","tid":176152,"uid":12286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T0