aces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9727801178ff2211e5bd9a1459f49897bcccec88","tid":176152,"uid":61370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T05:38:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不斷練就得，腹呢個部位可以狂練，做下捲腹、平板或者推滾輪</blockquote><br />\n有肚腩都得?<br />\n到時候個腩會唔會直接練做肌肉<br />\n咁咪會好漲?<br />\n多謝巴打解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做登山者 減左個肚腩就會見到腹肌"}]}